para_trans: Appointment to the post of Principal Chief Conservator of Forests (Head of Forest Force), Maharashtra State
Madam Cama Road, Hutatma Rajguru Chowk,
Government of Maharashtra is pleased to promote Smt. Shomita Biswas, Indian
Forest Service (1988) to the Apex Scale (Level 17 in Pay Matrix) and appoint her to the
post of Principal Chief Conservator of Forests (Head of Forest Force), Maharashtra State
Consequent to the retirement of Shri. Shailesh Tembhurnikar, L.F.S. at 31 ° July, 2024
Smt. Shomita Biswas, IFS shall accordingly assume the charge on 1 "August, 2024
This Government Order is available at the Government of Maharashtra's website
www.maharashtra.gov.in. Reference number for this is 202408011743163019
